@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as User
participant ":System" as System

activate User
User -> System : searchAircrafts(model, status, year)
activate System

note right of System: The system filters the existing\naircrafts based on the provided\noptional criteria.

System --> User : returns the filtered list of aircrafts
deactivate System
deactivate User
@enduml